HEADWORD: Surfboat
<hw>Surf"boat`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>A boat intended for use in heavy surf. It is built with a
pronounced sheer, and with a view to resist the shock of waves and of
contact with the beach.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Surfeit</ent>⟦br⟧
